re slippage.  This condition can vary by terrain type.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="Lxfk1!]!PYKOQZXEM`HW"><field name="NUM">20</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="|f5k=%bY%dE%vLyxYaXA"><field name="VAR" id="Pn4_q~v_/TkrLShW@pU.">accel_rate</field><comment pinned="false" h="109" w="459">This variable controls the rate of the acceleration ramp-- how long the bot takes to get from zero to max. In initial testing 1 worked well, 2 produced tire slippage.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="!Y#qq$N}V;4zKK+9[,Yn"><field name="NUM">1</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="QsNAc7NCM-=1M`L9Ee#E"><field name="VAR" id="`=ApUrD}(0qDd^Yp4(rh">max_normal_speed</field><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="}fN0}8jRw3LL]$JgxhiN"><field name="NUM">60</field></shadow></value><next><block type="variables_set" id="%=3rwy~1:`=4qfgu1+R;"><field name="VAR" id="Bdy2d{-@DtkKH1)=c_,-">max_turbo_speed</field><comment pinned="false" h="119" w="369">This value will determine the maximum speed to which the bot will accelerate before topping out. Valid range is 0 to 100.</comment><data>{"commentRefs":[],"fieldData":{"~commentOffsetX":"16","~commentOffsetY":"16"}}</data><value name="VALUE"><shadow type="math_number" id="?v_?~06Di}UAHnu$9g8z"><field name="NUM">99</field></shadow></value><next><block type="quest_Note_1_quest_Show_String_For_Note_Big_Func" id="h=c~37HWuAZ$r#MLG1n5"><value name="textStrIn"><shadow type="text" id="_Pu|@1%)RcWn`)s8n`bx"><field name="TEXT">Below, Setup Code for Student:</field></shadow></value></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></next></block></statement></bl